[h4 id=Level2.1:
 
	" Level 2.1:
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"At the start, a web is blocking the way to a shortcut. It usually requires 5 hits with the scythe to
	$LF
	"clean up, but I lower that number to only 2 thanks to the warrior glitch, since the axe has a shorter
	$LF
	"range, a bigger hitbox and hits in a circular motion in two steps, effectively hitting twice. This saves
	$LF
	"three hits. I pick up a clear potion and an axe to finish up this level.
	$LF
]p
