[h4 id=Level6.3:
 
	" Level 6.3:
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
]h4
[p 
	"The invisibility spell makes this level easier.
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"Getting one blue potion and a red one.
	$LF
	"That MOSQUITO boss normally requires, for the kill, to hop on the back of a mosquito (another
	$LF
	"mosquito) then wait until he enters a charging phase in order to land a hit, which takes a
	$LF
	"considerable amount of time and isn’t very entertaining either!!
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"So, I looked for a flaw to not only gain time, but also make this fight more fun...
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
	"...I’ll then engage him from the ground since I’ve noticed that he has the same movement patterns
	$LF
	"as INFERNO but way faster!!!
	$LF
	"The problem here is that the game proceeds to make mosquito-riding enemies spawn just for us to
	$LF
	"use them for the battle, and that creates lag. I had to kill those enemies as they spawned and were
	$LF
	"offscreen while still managing and attacking the boss without losing any frame.
	$LF
	"I’ve spent an insane amount of time and rerecords (2000+) just to get that done.
	$LF
]p
